{"tid":1598373,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"《免費送》光復香港黑旗/黑色區旗","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T20:21:05.000Z","uid":38677,"like":112,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"edb4d0fe08b97407c4137efe8720c467201315ec","tid":1598373,"uid":38677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9.29同10.1就到!!</span><br />\n為慶祝呢個普天同慶嘅大日子<br />\n我要振奮大家士氣！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我要周街都係黑旗！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">《免費送出》</span></strong>黑色旗36支俾各位巴絲打！<br />\n係我地團隊自己貼錢貼時間整（多謝L,C,K,M巴絲打）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZTEBUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZTEBUj.jpg&h=c11e4801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3C4o3zm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3C4o3zm.jpg&h=fbea824d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不過有以下條件先准攞：</span></strong></ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1）送俾你係比你拎出去行街購物用，拎去演唱會，拎去珠穆朗瑪峰，唔係比你擺屋企做display</span></strong></span><br />\n2）28/9號 指定時間地點交收（就唔到就下一個）<br />\n3）需要自己花少少時間完成字體修邊（送marker筆，我會教你）<br />\n4）需要自己DIY上旗杆/行山棍（教你）<br />\n5）做個出色嘅護旗手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要同意以上5點，喺度留低個telegram </span><br />\n名額有限<br />\n先到先得<br />\n請指明要邊款<br />\n如要區旗，請指明要唔要爆血custom option  <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者你可以考慮自己整:<br />\n<br />\n  光復香港 時代革命 黑旗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568640</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"039208c42923f75d41f5f3ae963ae53235c6ef2a","tid":1598373,"uid":138820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae05e83c99f173aa33be421abf0dd8301033421","tid":1598373,"uid":35746,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93becec684a62f49eb801fb0111ba1886970435f","tid":1598373,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:00:55.000Z","msg":"@gdei3739<br />\n<br />\n想要光復香港旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e15a2af4cfa1e83103aaf4a16582b5a579a89b0","tid":1598373,"uid":96465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"63261d1b04a6380f205c0a7fc522a9c94932548e","tid":1598373,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":