ces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d495fdf487731c5a3e5dbfdd0ce43bcbacf5c3b3","tid":1598373,"uid":310614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:49:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>得返最後幾塊黑區旗<br />\n留意有幾個條件<br />\n<br />\n今晚交收<br />\n<br />\n先到先得，留telegram<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e3c7005c034590618c5c3aa2622802835a6b0df9","tid":1598373,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f639461340593f905d97abbc718fa4ab2eacf3","tid":1598373,"uid":310614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位收到旗嘅䕶旗撚（多謝大家準時）</span></span><br />\n因為成本，時間同人手嘅限制，大家要花啲功夫完成<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>自己修邊：</strong></ins><br />\n一開始個字唔靚唔緊要，請用黑色marker ，跟住個字模/圖案收返靚d邊<br />\n如果係區旗，畫返塊花瓣中間條黑色線<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B0ijYLgpGHQEa3A3M3Y2cVl2MWRGR3g4enNBcU1FQVdNVTNn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0B0ijYLgpGHQEa3A3M3Y2cVl2MWRGR3g4enNBcU1FQVdNVTNn&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=48c585e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B0ijYLgpGHQEa3A3M3Y2cVl2MWRGR3g4enNBcU1FQVdNVTNn</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8odO5L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8odO5L.jpg&h=cc2be5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kdpVLR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kdpVLR.png&h=174f749a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>旗杆物料可以㨂 （for example ）</strong></ins><br />\n行山棍<br />\n竹枝<br />\n伸縮旗桿（五金/文具店）<br />\n驗樓空鼓棍（五金）即係詹sir驗樓鳩篤果支<br />\n涼衣申縮棍（家品店）<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>上桿有幾個方法，由最美觀開始計：</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n1）自己衣車/縫線整個幾個圈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxQckcN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxQckcN.jpg&h=115b45b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）用衣車整條空位放旗杆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoFPnrv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoFPnrv.png&h=b6485dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）用扣針<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kus2HrH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkus2HrH.png&h=c68f1313&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWrSkdr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWrSkdr.png&h=0a712c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n配合索帶，膠紙，扣針，自己諗掂佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果各位巴打有更好嘅提議請分享</span></span>"},{"pid":"600a90c126fe6d237a38a2e40b6ceb2a4613cf29","tid":1598373,"uid":7427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430519402b339352e5e12205c00ffde9a0f84779","tid":1598373,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c56e7391c2f9b8d6943212881819c13fbd7163d","tid":1598373,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"《行動》928 雨傘5週年 集會 yellow object<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590313</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51dfcfa4a67e6f08b248c1b55d6485013230e3c6","tid":1598373,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"環保可循環再用黑旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dn1Cice.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDn1Cice.gif&h=805da215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n1. 長遮<br />\n2. 黑tee （薄身比較好）<br />\n3. 夾 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HnZL71X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHnZL71X.jpg&h=ecf31717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n步驟：<br />\n1. 首先將兩個袖縮入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n83Es12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn83Es12.jpg&h=68f6bf60&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 將遮頭就咁隊入去，唔好穿出來<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Syj8mS7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSyj8mS7.jpg&h=83b7aad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 衫領位再摺多下先夾實<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja1e1Tj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja1e1Tj.jpg&h=9f9ae7af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuopEFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuopEFa.jpg&h=40124ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n縮骨遮都用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕帶長遮嘅都可以照升黑旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qNYKkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qNYKkn.jpg&h=dfc84728&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"43e82660c101ca54c10c38f860675f6e6cfb97ab","tid":1598373,"uid":122445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"正呀 推"},{"pid"